snippet.title: Maya Mystery | True Crime
snippet.description:
Hey! 👋 

I'm Maya & I am creating true crime YouTube videos. 

I like learning about real life cases and creating dialogue about the people behind them; 
I take information I've gathered & put it into video format.. with some thoughts of my own. 
If you like this channel and my videos; feel free to subscribe, the motivation will help me make more!

** THE OPINIONS IN THESE VIDEOS ARE MY OWN & ARE JUST THAT; MY OWN OPINIONS. 
NOT MEANT TO BE TAKEN FOR FACTS OR MEDICAL INFORMATION/DIAGNOSIS, THIS IS YOUTUBE, GUYS! **
